{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 RAPID\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Professional workflow automation for REAPER that automates track mapping, media import, and LUFS normalization.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Three Workflows\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Full Workflow}: Import + mapping + normalization in one pass\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Import Mode}: Map recording tracks to mix template (preserves FX, sends, routing)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Normalize Mode}: Standalone LUFS normalization on existing tracks\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Features\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Fuzzy matching with aliases for automatic track suggestions\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Multi-slot mapping with auto-duplicate for multiple sources\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab LUFS calibration system for creating custom normalization profiles\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Per-profile LUFS settings (segment size, percentile, threshold)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Offline media auto-relinking via progressive path suffix matching\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab MixnoteStyle dark theme\sa180\par}
